\[\frac{AP}{OP} = \frac{125}{r} \quad \text{and} \quad \frac{BQ}{OQ} = \frac{375\sqrt{2}}{h}.\]Hence,
\begin{align*}
AP &= \frac{125r}{\sqrt{r^2 + h^2}}, \\
BQ &= \frac{375\sqrt{2} h}{\sqrt{r^2 + h^2}}.
\end{align*}Also, by the Pythagorean Theorem,
\[OP = \sqrt{r^2 + h^2}.\]Therefore,
\begin{align*}
AP + BQ &= \frac{125r}{\sqrt{r^2 + h^2}} + \frac{375\sqrt{2} h}{\sqrt{r^2 + h^2}} \\
&= \frac{125r + 375\sqrt{2} h}{\sqrt{r^2 + h^2}}.
\end{align*}By the Pythagorean Theorem, $r^2 + h^2 = (600)^2 + (200\sqrt{7})^2 = 360000 + 280000 = 640000.$  Hence,
\[\frac{125r + 375\sqrt{2} h}{\sqrt{r^2 + h^2}} = \frac{125r + 375\sqrt{2} h}{800}.\]We want to minimize this expression, subject to the constraint $r^2 + h^2 = 640000.$

